---
/**
 * "In production" stub for journal entries whose body isn't published yet.
 * Mirrors the same editorial register as work/InProduction so the experience
 * stays consistent across collections.
 */
---
<section class="px-5 sm:px-6 md:px-8 pt-12 md:pt-20 pb-12 md:pb-16">
  <div class="mx-auto text-center max-w-(--container-prose)">
    <div
      class="font-mono uppercase text-label text-text-muted inline-flex items-baseline gap-2.5 mb-9 tracking-mono-x"
    >
      <span aria-hidden="true">↳</span>
      <span>Status</span>
    </div>
    <h2
      class="font-serif font-350 m-0 mb-12 tracking-display-xl text-balance"
      style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); line-height: 1.05;"
    >
      This entry is <span class="italic">in production.</span>
    </h2>
    <p
      class="font-sans m-0"
      style="font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.3vw, 1.2rem); line-height: 1.7;"
    >
      The full essay will be published soon. In the meantime, read
      {" "}<a href="/journal/long-form-short-form" class="border-b border-current hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-300 pb-px">On the long-form / short-form rhythm of a brand system</a>{" "}
      — the first piece in the series.
    </p>
    <div class="font-mono text-text-muted mt-20 text-lg" style="letter-spacing: 0.4em;">— — —</div>
  </div>
</section>
